        <p>There are two ways to start a new integration task:</p>

        <ol>
            <li>The STD connects to an external source, imports the data and generates a &quot;diff&quot; from the previous import, pushing it to the Flux Capacitor</li>

            <li>Smaller (diff) changed portions are hooked directly into Flux Capacitor for processing</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <%= link_to image_tag("rules_flow.png", {width: 640}), image_path('rules_flow.png') %><br>
